1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,160
I remember old wood like something from the 1950s, worn with age.

2
00:00:05,160 --> 00:00:09,200
I remember inside when necklaces, earrings and a photograph.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:14,240
I remember a man in a grey suit and a woman with a forced smile stared back.

4
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:16,160
I remember the man's eyes.

5
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,240
They followed them.

6
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:20,240
I remember the same figure from their nightmares.

7
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:22,480
I remember their mother quickly closed it.

8
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:25,680
I remember eventually she sold it after moving.

9
00:00:25,680 --> 00:00:28,680
My mother never understood what happened that last week.

10
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:30,960
I remember was it the house?

11
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,840
I remember the jewelry box.

12
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,240
I remember something else entirely.

13
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:38,840
I remember whatever it was she still checks under her bed.

14
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,560
I remember always.

15
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:44,360
I remember because you never know who would need punishment next.

16
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:48,040
If I ever tell this story again, it means I made it out.
